long_description    3D Scientific Data Visualization and Plotting using VTK as the \
    rendering backend and pyqt5/pyqt4/pyside2 for the (G)UI.

license             BSD
platforms           darwin

checksums           rmd160  ef687370510534b296709e6b0eb22ca485f6ed8a \
